BEGIN:VEVENT
IMAGE;VALUE=URI;DISPLAY=BADGE;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://hermannpark.org/wp
 -content/uploads/2024/04/japanese_garden_2__-_photo_by_patrick_talley-scal
 ed.jpg
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://hermannpark.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/0
 4/japanese_garden_2__-_photo_by_patrick_talley-scaled.jpg
UID:5pNxgQZREJdMwCR3CimFU
SUMMARY:Japanese Garden Volunteer Day
DTSTAMP:20260629T025250Z
DTSTART:20260709T090000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us every Thursday for hands-on gardening projects at the J
	apanese Garden. From 9 a.m. to 12 p.m.\, come help with seasonal tasks lik
	e planting\, weeding\, mulching\, and pruning. A great way to connect with
	 others and make a visible impact in the Park! \nNo experience needed. All
